<sec id="id-7253e830-61c9-4fe4-f44c-e91a5304dc36"><title><bold><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="339c8c9e-e6ed-4618-fc88-6a1dc86676f4" timestamp="1667316190878"?>Example of gender budgeting in a local authority<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="339c8c9e-e6ed-4618-fc88-6a1dc86676f4"?></bold></title><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="8e7ded49-1aef-4bf8-8060-6a6e0e4552f6" text="[Former Box 24]" timestamp="1675426985679"?><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="4eed20f2-d771-4f13-aaec-71b25eb0a17b" timestamp="1667316166032"?>For several years, an organization has been helping a group of local authorities in Belgium to implement a gender-responsive budgetary policy, which has been required under national law since 2007.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="4eed20f2-d771-4f13-aaec-71b25eb0a17b"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="cefb7853-714f-4a28-ccbc-c2d8d42e7c71" timestamp="1667316166032"?>This organization helps the local authorities to analyse the impact of public funding on gender inequality, with a view to drawing up a budget in line with the categories defined under national law. For example, they should consider the impact on the respective situations of <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="cefb7853-714f-4a28-ccbc-c2d8d42e7c71"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="d429a19c-d6b7-4f48-bd0b-c71622edc66f" timestamp="1669040362472"?>wo<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="d429a19c-d6b7-4f48-bd0b-c71622edc66f"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="e86f47ab-c851-4718-a4a9-a7bfe14541e2" timestamp="1667316166032"?>men and <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="e86f47ab-c851-4718-a4a9-a7bfe14541e2"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="824b74ab-3a20-49c8-cb35-f36a99c295a7" text="wo" timestamp="1669040366140"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="b1da1b12-53c3-4838-fd6b-f14d8531206f" timestamp="1667316166032"?>men of expenditure on investments in a new public lighting system, especially in terms of safety.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="b1da1b12-53c3-4838-fd6b-f14d8531206f"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="b2d4b685-636f-4df9-dc64-67fa761971ad" timestamp="1667316166031"?>Other local authorities, which already have a strong command of this categorization, should optimize and implement this approach.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="b2d4b685-636f-4df9-dc64-67fa761971ad"?></p><p/></sec>